Giam5-lo5-ong5 phai3 siau2-kui2-a2 khi3 iong5-kan chau2-chhoe7 beng5-i: “Hoan7-na7 mng5-khau2 bo5 oan-hun5--e5 chiu7-si7 beng5-i.” 
Siau2-kui2-a2 lai5 kau3 iong5-kan, chhoe7 chin-choe7 piN7-iN7, mng5-khau2 long2 u7 chin-choe7 oan-hun5.  Choe3-au7, i khoaN3-kiN3 chit8-keng, mng5-khau2 kan-na7 u7 chit8-chiah oan-hun5, siau2-kui2-a2 chiu7 kong2: “Chit-e5 it-teng7 si7 beng5-i”.  Au7--lai5 chit8-e7 tham3-thiaN chiah chai chit-keng piN7-iN7, cha-hng chiah khai-giap8 nia7. 
U7 chit8-e5 thak8-chheh-lang5, siang-peng5 e5 chhu3-piN si7 phah-thih kap phah-tang5--e5, tak8-jit8 chha2 kah beh si2.  Thak8-chheh lang5 chiu7 ka7 siang-peng5 e5 chhu3-piN kong2: “lin2 na7 kheng2 poaN khi3 pat8-ui7, goa2 chiu7 pan7 chit8-toh-a2 chhiaN2--lin2”.  Bo5 goa7-ku2, siang-peng5 e5 chhu3-piN long2 hoaN-hi2 tap-eng3.  Thak8-chheh lang5 ia7 chiau3 iok-teng7 chhiaN2--in.  Che7-toh e5 si5, thak8-chheh lang5 mng7 khoaN3 in beh poaN khi3 to2-ui7.  In kong2, phah-thih--e5 beh poaN koe3 phah-tang5--e5 chit-peng5, phah-tang5--e5 beh poaN koe3 phah-thih--e5 hit-peng5.  
Ho2-giah8 lang5: “Goa2 u7-chiN5, li2 ai3 phou5 goa2 chiah tioh8.” 
San3-hiong lang5: “U7-chiN5 si7 lin2 tau e5 tai7-chi3, kap goa2 long2 bo5 kan-gai7, goa2 na2-tioh8 phou5 li2 ?”
Ho2-giah8 lang5: “Goa2 na7 chiN5 chit8-poaN3 hou7 li2, li2 kam2 m7-bian2 tioh8 phou5 goa2 ?”
San3-hiong lang5: “An2-ni m7-bian2 tioh8 phou5 li2, li2 chiN5 chit8-poaN3 hou7 goa2, lan2 chiu7 piN5-piN5 ho2-giah8 ah, phou5 li2 beh chhong3 siaN2 ?”
Ho2-giah8 lang5: “Ho2, ka2-su2 goa2 sou2-u7 e5 chiN5 long2-chong2 hou7 li2, li2 kam2 kaN2 bo5 phou5 goa2 ?”
San3-hiong lang5: “Chhio3 phoa3 lang5 e5 chhui3, na7 an2-ni goa2 pian3 ho2-giah8, li2 pian3 san3-chhiah.  Tian-to3 si7 li2 tioh8 lai5 phou5 goa2 chiah tioh8 ......” 
Ho2-giah8 lang5: “Goa2 u7 1000 ban7 e5 chai5-san2.” 
San3-chhiah lang5: “Bo5 hi-han2, goa2 ma7 u7 1000 ban7.” 
Ho2-giah8 lang5: “Mai3 teh pun5 ke-kui ......” 
San3-chhiah lang5: “HuiN5-tit8 li2 u7-chiN5 to tang3-sng m7-bat teh eng7, kap goa2 bo5 chiN5 thang eng7 m7-si7 long2 kang7-khoan2 ?”
Chit8-e5 hoe5-siuN7 kap chit8-e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kang7-che7 chit8-chiah chun5, it-tit8 khoaN3 hu7-jin5-lang5. Hu7-jin5-lang5 siu7-khi3, chiu7 kio3 lang5 phah hoe5-siuN7, hoe5-siuN7 chiu7 bak8-chiu kheh-kheh m7-kaN2 koh khoaN3, bo5-ku2, chun5 oa2 hoaN7, hu7-jin5-lang5 koh kio3 lang5 ka7 phah.  Hoe5-siuN7 mng7 kong2: “Goa2 bak8-chiu kheh-kheh, si7 an2-choaN2 koh leh phah goa2 ?” Hu7-jin5-lang5 in3 kong2 “Li2 bak8-chiu kheh-kheh si7 teh siuN7 goa2 e5 bi2-mau7.” 
Chit8-e5 lang5 e5 kha hou7 chiN3 sia7--tioh8, khi3 chhoe7 i-seng.  I-seng chiu7 ka7 chiN3 thou2--chhut-lai5 goa7-khau2 e5 pou7-hun7 ki3 hou7 tng7.  hoan7-chia2 mng7: “Tiau5 ti7 kha lai7-te2--e5 beh an2-choaN2 ?” I-seng in3 kong2: “Goa2 chia si7 goa7-kho, tiau5 ti7 lai7-te2--e5, li2 ai3 chhoe7 lai7-kho.” 
(Hong-hiong3 Te7 15 ki5, 1992 ni5 3 goeh8)
